
<DOCTYPE!>
<html>
<head>
	<title>SpeakUp</title>
</head>
<body>
	<div>
		<h2>Welcome to SpeakUp:
		<br>
		The Virtual Suggestion Box for Students to Log Bullying Concerns</h2>
	 </div> 
	 <div>
		<h3>Bullying: What You Need to Know</h3>
		<ul>
			<li>What is bullying?</li>
			<li>What's the difference between bullying on vs. offline?</li>
			<li>What to do if you are being bullied</li>
			<li>What to do if your friend is being bullied</li>
			<li>What to do if your friend is a bully</li>
		</ul>

	<h3> All of your Concerns </h3>
		<ul>
			<% @concerns.each do |c| %>
			<li>
				<%= link_to 'Edit', edit_user_concern_path(current_user, c.id) %>
				<%= link_to 'Delete', user_concern_path(current_user, c.id), method: :delete %>
				<%= c.text %>
			</li>
			<% end %>
		</ul>

		</div> 
	</div>
</body>
</html>